Seyni rimata Jesus xye pirana raluk-hepomhaletluna hiyáhoni wla htshinatkana: — Hixlahe hepomhakaka hixkakluko klu ntshinatkahi xye hima tshinanu, Xekoyakapa hi hetanno seyni howukchiniyaka hetanutnakno?
Wanna hi xye tshijne hajenetkani, hita xye tshijne hajeru nmixyawakanutka pixka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Ptowruneko hetanu nunkaklewjeta. Ptowru judeu hapatjexyawaka hanjihohnewakapji hiyrunu Hoyakalupji, nunkaklewjekanaxya. Nunkaklewaxyawaka hikeklu nyohimata.
Waneya Pilatos wla tshinru: — Haklu tshinanhe hi piynumsatno? Hi he pimata hita himukata towutletlu cruz pupniywakapa ho puchoxikowakapa?
Waneya Jesus-ni mane hkochtshekna, mkatshri sama, linho sama, phamlu pahiru yapjetkaluroyma ruwtokluna. Wan-rixjetna judeu-ne hkapnaxikowakapa tshinanu.
Waneya Tomé wan-tshinru Jesus: — Nutsrukate! Noyakalute!
haté tenhohne ranikkoklunutka papko pirana potuko. Waneya Jesus tenhohne hma yaknuklunuwa ruykotna jejine, hnurrene, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru mixkonuyma waneya tenhohne ranikkatka Jesus.
Waneya wale sejirtshi hjeminna, rapatjemtna. Rimyekamtna klu tshinanu satkaka yineru jemlu waleko htokanu, nuretkalune yanumakanaxinri.
Mapa Mil Yine Batiza-xikowaka PiranapniWale tshinanu rimatankoxluna ptowruneka israel-nerune waleko Jesus cruz rutaklerna, Hoyakalu halikaka hitakatkalu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa hiyrun-koxa Messias rixyawaka.
