Potuk-hapolu hyapanu, hma muwajyawakanupa seyni rutskalajikolupni halikaka myankatu.
Klu tshinanu hewi xye tshijneya hi wimwalu satu poktshi hwahohnekanatatshripa. Seyni wkahwakanru poktshi hwahohnekanatatshri pnu hichpajikatshri.
Hoyakalu Tokanu Hepixle PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune nuchinikanune, hichinikanretanru xye. Ptowrunek-yine yijnakhapkatatshinephi seyni hi yanumhapkatatshinephi, hi jihekanuwhapkatatshinephi.
Hi he hetlu hanurixa hepixkota halixlu Abraão kamhaleru kihleru tshinanu? Kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu hike mmahaxikatni ralixle.
Hoyakalustsi hapokanu, waneya hixastsi hyanu Hoyakalu. Hixa hektuwaka kamhatshinhi heromyohinwa! Hixachatatshinhi, hepi hchinikanurunhi hpowrathajixinwa!
<font color=teal>1 Pedro</font>Hali HichinikluneHita Pedro-no Jesus Cristo nurrerno. Twu yonawahlo judeu-ne mwachatkane tshinanupa. Ponto tshijne yatshine tshinanu, Galácia tshijne yatshine tshinanu, Capadócia tshijne yatshine tshinanu, Ásia tshinikowaka yatshine tshinanu, Bitínia tshinikowaka yatshine tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu xye koxa htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Hetanu, Sião tshinikowaka nutakanru sotlu hijhakaluru pixkalut-potu, psolupjiko poyehiwkakatshri. Sotlu nuretkaluru halukalur-potu. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru potuko halixatshri hi hmahijerutanu.”
Rujhalu hektutu hkatjixini. Raluklu kihlewaka hkamhiywaka halikaka. Rujhalu kihlewaka rawyawaka hiyrunu romkahpotuxyawaklu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hixa salewnatshinhi Hoyakalu halujyawaka tshinanu, hiwekle henekanru Hoyakalu ruslahyawakaplu. Klu tshinanu walekni hiyakotatshri himat-hislahatshri kihleru wkamhaleru tshinanu.
Tsru Himukatatshri Potukni Hoyakalu TokanuWutsrukate Jesus Cristo pixkonu pirana hiyrunu rapojinri pirana wunkajinixkahi mitshi, hi tsrunni pirana, yineko hchinikanu pirana, chinikantshi heneklewatatshri pirana phuta wtshinatkahi mitshi. Klu tshinanu hix-honra rumukatle ptowru potuko himukatatshri hetatshinpotukwu.
Xye hapka himatanu, hnikawnahohnexini klu papko, runanna Hoyakalu tokanu heyikatshinepa wannako hichinikanu halukanru homkahitatshinepa.
Seyni katukta kamhajetlu Hoyakalu tokanu, halikaka Hoyakalu hamotle wale yehi rawanutka. Wan-rixikowaka tshinanu wimata Hoyakaluymalunetkawu:
Ptowru yineru Cristo-ymalutu hi hektuwaka hkamhajeta. Halikaka hektuwaka kamhatshri katuktako, hi retjetlu Cristo hiyrun-koxa hi rimathetlu.
Hi satuknako yineru hetawalu Hoyakalu, hikeklu. Seyni wuchinikkajiniklunu hixaymalu Hoyakalu hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hamotle hiphujetka hixaya.
Mturune pixkalune, hislahinwa mayawletshicha hma momkahixyawakanupa.
Halixlu Tshinanu Jmererunepwu PiranapniNuchinikanune, nuchinikanrexinixkalu mitshi nyonanwakaxyawakaphi nasrujyawakaphi hiwejikaluru pirana ptowru yineru tshinanupa, netlu hijhakalur-koxni nyonanwakaxyawakaphi ntowuxyahi jmerpotuphi halixlu hasrujikolu pirana hislahpotutanu. Xye halixlu Hoyakalu pa katapka henekna hinerune, ralixjene.
Hitni mitshikananu hwatshrino hiyrun-koxa hmahle hwatshrino. Yinuwakatshrino hiyrunu hmahaxyawak-potuko hwatshrino htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, ptowru himukatatshrino, xawakni hohne hwatshrino, mitshikawluru hwatshri hiyrunu xawakni hohne pnutpatka hwatshrino.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Tiatira Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Tiatira poktshi hajene kosekatshri: “Xye pirana runkakhi Hoyakalu Whene, tshitshmero pixka hixayhaletatshri hiyrunu yomuwa bronze hixirikkaluru hatajnu pixka hixatshri hiyrunu hatawnajixitatshri.
Nuchinikanune pejnu ntshihetjeta, nsaletjeta. Hiyáhoni jmererunephi hehchinikanuxyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni netatka. Waneya cavalo klatalo neta. Hiyrunu cavalo yapatshri kachritwa hanikamtatka. Waneya phuru sahye renekka. Hiyáhoni hyatka hallirewatatshri, rallirewaxyawakapa.
Wale tshinanu Hoyakalu tuplawakle yoptowaka sreta rawna. Hoyakalu towre hkamhajetna Hoyakalupjiya hohi, hoyetshno. Pohirtshi tuplawakle tuplatatshri wannayma hwanu.
Waneya ruchotkatkana hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene quatro. Nyi quatro Hoyakalu halpoklenni wale papko potuko tshinanu, wale mhale, wale ksuru, wale hora potuko tshinanupa yine ruylaxyawakapna, satupka mapate (1/3) yine pejnu.
Waneklukawa potuko tsru hiyoliklu tshiji rixa. Waneya satupka dez-te (1/10) tsru poktshi psojite yawnapjitana. Hiyoliklu tshiji tshinanu sete mil yinni hipnana. Pimrine hpikpotutanna. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu tenhohne hajeru rimalwutna.
Himukatlu renekka Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene hkamnixyawakapa, rallixyawakapna. Hiyrunu towuwlu renekka ptowru nerune, ptowru nrukaka yanumatatshine hiyrunu ptowru tshijne hajene htowuxyawakapa.
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hamlu uva tshiji hwatshri, hitaklu hamapiyma, tshij-hoho hajeru. Waneya ruknoklu uva katsohapi yehi, Hoyakalu jhekanu yehi ruknokna.
Waneya sotluha tenhohne hichpajikatshri, yine hoho rapokatka. Tsru tshrajhakakalu, quarenta kilo pa hinnu hetkolu satkaka sotluha. Waneya yine hektuwaka htshinanwakatluna Hoyakalu sotluha hsalexyawakna tshinanu, klu tshinanu tsru potuklu xye salewnalu.
Hike hanjitanru ruchanremkana ouro, prata, sotlujikaka kwenur-potu, tuwutu pérola-ji. Hiyrunu mkatshri phayamtalu linho-mta, hi mkatshri seroluko, hi hepramtalu seda-mtako, hi carneiro pixi serolu kamhikoluko, hi hahmuna kihleruko, hi rapkajere kamhikolu pajiko, hi hahmuna kwenuru kamhikolu pajkaka, hi bronze kamhikaluru, hi yomuwa, hi sotlu chpata kwenuruko ranjitkatkana.
Hinanu hnikapyawakaplu pohirtshinni hitu, soldado-ne kosekatshinni hitu, soldado-nni hitu, cavalo-nni hitu hiyrunu cavalo-nni yapakanatatshinni hitu hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yinni hitu, towrertshinni hitu, mtowutkonni hitu, yinni hijhakalunni hitu, yinni mujhakonni hitu hnikanu.
Satu tsru cerca tenolu potuko, hichyatlu poktshi. Doze jihlojikowakkaka rimwa cerca. Doze koxna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene cerca hiphaptote hinotatshine. Jihlojikowakkaka hichyapre rawa hiwaktshikaka yonatkaluru. Doze israel-nerune xkehi wane hwahiwakata.
Seyni poktshi malekate rawna kawene pa himtuknurune, kahontshine, kapoklewaklerune, jiylalewaklerune, mayawletshicha kahwakpiratatshine, hayloklewlu halukatshine hiyrunu weyawlu kamhatshine.
